**Key Features:**
- Clean message bubbles with subtle borders
- Timestamp below each message (small, gray text)
- Model indicator shows which model responded
- ðŸ”’ icon indicates local processing
- Inline document references (tappable cards)
- Streaming cursor for real-time responses
- Voice and attachment buttons always visible

**Interaction States:**
- Message tap: Select/copy text
- Long press message: Copy, regenerate, delete options
- Swipe message left: Quick delete
- Document reference tap: Open document preview
- Model indicator tap: Show model info

