## Launch Checklist

### Pre-Launch (Week -4)
- [ ] TestFlight beta with 50-100 users
- [ ] Gather feedback and testimonials
- [ ] Create App Store screenshots (all sizes)
- [ ] Record demo video (30-60 seconds)
- [ ] Write App Store description
- [ ] Set up landing page
- [ ] Prepare press kit

### Launch Week
- [ ] Submit to App Store (aim for Thursday release)
- [ ] Product Hunt submission
- [ ] Post to relevant subreddits
- [ ] Email beta users
- [ ] Social media announcements
- [ ] Monitor reviews and respond

### Post-Launch (Week +1 to +4)
- [ ] Daily review monitoring
- [ ] Rapid bug fixes if needed
- [ ] User feedback analysis
- [ ] Plan first update based on feedback
- [ ] Begin content marketing (blog posts)
- [ ] Reach out to press/reviewers

